snippet.title: Meghan Markle Recalls Struggling Actress Days on the Ellen Show... lying for dramatics?
snippet.description:
Meghan Markle has made a surprise appearance on the Ellen Show after both her and Prince Harry's bombshell interview on Oprah earlier this year. 

Continuing the saga of how Meghan grew up struggling with cash - according to her and that letter she sent US politicians about treating herself to $5 salads, we find Meghan recalling the days of her broken down car that she didn't have any money to fix. 

It's interesting that the girl who grew up going to prestigious private schools all her life and who's father is a winner of 2 Emmys, claims that she had a struggling life. Let's discuss!
